# Jitter diagnostic — host. Walks RIGHT at constant velocity for
# the entire match. Pairs with 2p_jitter.client.shot which sits
# still and screenshots burst-style so we can see whether the
# host's mech (as the client sees it) moves smoothly or jitters.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/jitter_host
network host 24041
name HostA

at 150 press right
at 150 shot match_start
at 700 shot late
at 800 end
